HEADWORD: Water dressing
<hw>Wa"ter dress"ing</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <fld>(Med.)</fld> <def>The
treatment of wounds or ulcers by the application of water; also, a
dressing saturated with water only, for application to a wound or an
ulcer.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Water dropwort</ent>⟦br⟧
